data.name: label1.Text
data.value:
You make your way to the tallest structure located right at the middle of the town and decide to enter. The eeriness of silence embrace you as soon as you arrive at the Town Hall.
The wind was blowing briskly, making the weak, dead limbs of the tree snap off. It doesn't appear like anything is wrong at first glance, but you feel somethingwas off.
